[normal]’
[normal] only programme has: 
[normal]In 2013, the indoor competition had entries of 1500 teams (a 32% increase on 2012) from the U13 and U15 age groups; whilst the club competition had circa 400 entries from a variety of soft and hard ball formats ranging from U11 to U15. 
[normal] 
[normal]The co
[normal]mpetition has engaged with over 110
[normal],
[normal]000 girls since its introduction in 2003.The competition is administered centrally by ECB but supported locally by 39 CC
[normal]Bs
