[normal] 
[normal]affiliated clubs had 
[normal]a 
[normal]w
[normal]omen’s
[normal] and/
[normal] 
[normal]or 
[normal]g
[normal]irl’s sections
[normal] and by 
[normal]2012 
[normal]this had increased to 
[normal]565:
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Our ambition is to ensure the game maintains this level of growth and as such we are in the process of putting together a new strategy which will see the women’s cricket 
[normal]embedded
[normal] across our C
[normal]CB 
[normal]network to sustain and grow our network of clubs and increase the level of participation. 
